# 5) Thêm handler cho 2 nút mới

## Dán vào phần `USER HANDLERS`

```python
@dp.message(lambda m: m.text and match_key(m.text, "btn_888"))
async def menu_888(message: Message):
    await get_or_create_user_from_tg(message.from_user)
    lang = await get_user_lang(message.from_user.id)
    await send_vip_888(message, lang)


@dp.message(lambda m: m.text and match_key(m.text, "btn_vip_bot"))
async def menu_vip_bot(message: Message):
    await get_or_create_user_from_tg(message.from_user)
    lang = await get_user_lang(message.from_user.id)
    await send_vip_bots(message, lang)
```

